    "I believe that good science is not about being right, but about being better and using all the knowledge we can find to solve a piece of the puzzle, even if that means finding out the puzzle is missing important pieces.To answer the question of this commentary: \"To use or not to use?\"",
    "My answer is: GenAI is a tool.",
    "And you can use this tool to aid your thinking process, to get started when that blank page is staring at you or when you need to smooth things over.",
    "But, be careful with choosing the right tool for your purpose and do not forget to edit, fact check, refine and use your own voice and critical thinking to create the final synthesis of the information.",
    "Be aware of the limitations of your tool and, most importantly, like any other tool you have listed in your methods, GenAI is a tool that needs to be acknowledged."
